g.text: Directly responsible for the design and fabrication of museum exhibits, facility operations, mobile museum exhibits and satellite museum location development.

Created the plans and models for 6,000 sq. ft. of indoor exhibits and 7,500-sq. ft. of outdoor exhibits & space. Completed a $3.25M capital campaign for exhibits, operations and building purchase. Assisted in all major grant writing for this period and interfaced directly with most donors and community partners to help grow the museums attendance from 15k to 65k in 4 years and hit 100k in 2016 with record year-over-year growth (40-60%) for 5 years in a row.
